    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【阿达三国志（战棋版）】是由阿达游戏精心制作的一款三国题材的回合制策略战棋游戏。三国题材的魅力在于调兵遣将、攻防转换，而战棋玩法可以完美的适配这一点，于是我们便做了这样一次尝试。在这款战棋游戏里，您作为主公，可以招揽三国群英，组建一支梦幻阵容，以最小的兵损、最少的时间、最优的策略攻克一座座城池，最终一统天下。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意：本游戏包含内购，为了适配steam版本，我们推出平台专属优惠：在本平台游戏，登陆后前七天，每天送680元宝+68积分（等价68元充值）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方qq群：814524770 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作回归传统的战棋玩法，抛弃了复杂的地形和天气系统，而在兵种特性、攻击范围和技能设计的层面花了更多心思，易上手的同时，也保证了足够的策略性。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骑兵高机动，弓兵打得远，枪兵打两格，盾兵打斜角 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/7cce63741418f89abcc42985d462da20.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=550 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查看敌将的攻击范围和技能，知己知彼方能百战百胜 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/90b845e2cc6eba16d9bd8a7e87b76279.poster.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=750 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/90b845e2cc6eba16d9bd8a7e87b76279.webm?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/90b845e2cc6eba16d9bd8a7e87b76279.mp4?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用武将的技能组合，打出完美配合 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/e0afbbf4e9f7c45d81957837d4ee0f19.poster.avif?t=1741754252\" width=478 height=750 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/e0afbbf4e9f7c45d81957837d4ee0f19.webm?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/e0afbbf4e9f7c45d81957837d4ee0f19.mp4?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*武将</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武将是战力的核心，超过800名出场武将，每个武将都有自己的核心技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可额外学习强力技能，并装配符合武将特性的装备，自定义您的武将养成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 800+的三国武将池，组建梦幻阵容                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/91a9d25a93acacfceddf5cbd45e3a843.poster.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=750 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/91a9d25a93acacfceddf5cbd45e3a843.webm?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百个可自由学习的战斗技能，展示搭配策略</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/1db0b0d58da5c428830c2b403ff5b5c8.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=688 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*兵力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兵力是战斗的基础，武将需带兵方能出战，阵亡兵力需耗费资源才能补充。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >珍惜一兵一卒，携大军兵临城下</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/0c53f8876900fae5776849d9aa9ac578.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=646 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*内政</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修明内政方为长久之计，结合您的推图策略，规划专属内政方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级城建等级，提高资源产出</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/d49045b0109787f26e850db31711378e.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点出军事科技，助力攻城略地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/3893e7b283da2c50d5d22eefb8456178.avif?t=1741754252\" width=466 height=802 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >委任内政官员，政务事半功倍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/2dd198622dfe80e22c26a4ea2965b7f1.poster.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=750 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/2dd198622dfe80e22c26a4ea2965b7f1.webm?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/2dd198622dfe80e22c26a4ea2965b7f1.mp4?t=1741754252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*特色玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作在玩法上精益求精，力求为玩家们提供极具三国特色的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以最少的兵力、最短回合数通关，策略榜上把名扬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/a50dd8b5ab4307f3126f491c57efa278.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=682 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演武台上与玩家对弈，获得对方的武将</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/07c99c9e82c159b6265bba996b894aa4.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=748 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讨伐战还原历史经典战役，多路大军轮番进攻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/cb3825e4c87a513d474e181d2f372c24.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=832 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武将专属副本，操纵历史名将，重现经典瞬间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168890/extras/fd74630b56f407a517c260b637264591.avif?t=1741754252\" width=468 height=828 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三国憾系列互动剧情关卡陆续更新，若能重来，刘封是否会救关羽，诸葛亮能否完成兴复汉室的伟业，这一切由你决定。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您积十年之粮，携五虎上将，统百万大军，讨董卓、破河北、战曹操、下江东，一路攻城略地，一统天下之后，本作的乐趣才刚刚开始。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当无数玩家组成联盟，在上百座城池的大地图上彼此攻伐，您和您的将士会起到怎样的作用呢？让我们拭目以待！</p>",
